import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, TextField, Button, Box, Grid } from '@mui/material';

function SignUp() {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="sm" sx={{ paddingY: 8 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" align="center" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', fontWeight: 'bold', marginBottom: 4 }}>
        Create Your Account
      </Typography>
      <Box component="form">
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              label="Name"
              variant="outlined"
              required
              sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              label="Email"
              type="email"
              variant="outlined"
              required
              sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              label="Password"
              type="password"
              variant="outlined"
              required
              sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              label="Confirm Password"
              type="password"
              variant="outlined"
              required
              sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Button
              fullWidth
              variant="contained"
              size="large"
              sx={{
                backgroundColor: '#2a5e4f',
                color: '#ffffff',
                paddingY: 1.5,
                borderRadius: '25px',
                boxShadow: '0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)',
                '&:hover': { backgroundColor: '#204c3d' },
              }}
            >
              Sign Up
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default SignUp;
